text: Lesnoy () is a rural locality (a village) in Milovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 15 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Ufa, 12 km from Milovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Lesnoy, Republic of Bashkortostan
